('tkt_overnight_lib01', 'Knowledge base quality audit — validate all promoted shards', 'Audit quality of all promoted knowledge shards. 1) Query all promoted shards. 2) Evaluate accuracy, quality_score, categorization, search metadata. 3) Check for duplicates/near-duplicates. 4) Check for stale shards (>30 days, outdated). 5) Verify pack organization. Use substrate_db_query. Create findings for quality issues. Do NOT create new shards, audit quality only.', 'open', 'medium', 'quality', '01KGXG4SSG50D7HRJ811F6XZ3X', 'Librarian', true, 'human', '{"overnight_batch": true}')

